"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-lifestyle-fashion-olympics-paris-best-celebrity-looks-ariana-grande-mick-jagger-princess-anne-b1173663.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lifestyle|Fashion  Sign up for the best picks from our travel, fashion and lifestyle writers.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All eyes are on Paris as the2024 Olympics Gamesare fully underway - but as the global sporting elite battle it out for medals to bring home, who is shining in the stands?\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7190344071178153e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games attract the world's great and good every four years, but it's landing in the birthplace of couture calls for the chicest in recent memory (starting withthe medal trays, courtesy of Louis Vuitton).\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8921105519261166e-26, \"text\": \"The Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1948_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.341748900600119e-41, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the A-list have turned out.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At theOpening Ceremony, Chrissy Teigen and John Legend - both wearing Vuitton, one of the Games' prominent sponsors - lead arrivals, alongside Ariana Grande, who wore a Glinda-pink, Thom Browne princess gown with Swarovski jewels, and Cynthia Erivo, in an Elphaba-emerald green Vuitton dress; the pair continue their method-dressing promotion of Wicked, which comes in November.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chrissy Teigen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrissy_Teigen\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7668846532543564e-44, \"text\": \"Swarovski\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swarovski\"}, {\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also there was Serena Williams, in a tomato red Dolce & Gabbana dress, Emma Chamberlain, in archive Ralph Lauren pedal pushers and bar jacket, and Kaia Gerber, who wore a steel-grey mini dress by French designer Marine Serre.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dolce_&_Gabbana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dolce & Gabbana\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dolce_&_Gabbana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dolce_&_Gabbana\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0352835601946235e-14, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9863764182471385, \"rank\": 0.011617152453914394, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Serre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marine Serre\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Serre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Serre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stars took to cheering their fellow countrymen in the days that followed.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 27,Sir Mick Jaggerlent into Succession-style with a navy cap and non-branded grey hoodie - not a disimilar outfit to the cap, white shirt and blazer Nicole Kidman opted for to watch the Women's Street Final Skateboarding with husband, Keith Urban, and their two daughters the next day.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.644366938733039e-61, \"text\": \"Nicole Kidman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5238860238279034e-39, \"text\": \"Keith Urban\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sunday's Artistic Gymnastics Women's Qualification, which saw the United States' Simone Biles amaze the crowd, pulled in the Hollywood heavy-weights.Tom Cruise, in a bright white polo, waved to crowds, while Jessica Chastain wore a Ralph Lauren knit brandishing the Stars and Stripes flag.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9974254362157565, \"rank\": 0.0025812087195180348, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998244456883927, \"rank\": 0.00017537717576917764, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.2476676143672e-13, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.779586932921221e-45, \"text\": \"Jessica Chastain\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\"}, {\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0352835601946235e-14, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also there was Anna Wintour with Baz Luhrmann, and Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo in - bien s\\u00fbr!\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Wintour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.376484423586278e-64, \"text\": \"Anna Wintour\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Wintour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Wintour\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baz_Luhrmann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Baz Luhrmann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baz_Luhrmann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baz_Luhrmann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- yet more pink and green.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for royal sightings, Prince Albert II of Monaco and Princess Charlene of Monaco made an appearance at the Opening Ceremony while the King and Queen of the Netherlands were seen, sporting Just Stop Oil-hue orange, as they hollered during the women's preliminary round volleyball match, on July 29.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2267, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"score\": 0.9999492494762376, \"rank\": 5.074266765342835e-05, \"text\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\"}, {\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_War_II\", \"score\": 0.9998838713427237, \"rank\": 0.00011614202984909738, \"text\": \"II\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_War_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_War_II\"}, {\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9999999996766746, \"rank\": 3.232049650760836e-10, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9999999996766746, \"rank\": 3.232049650760836e-10, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 2394, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9267964307775782, \"rank\": 0.07896484183638418, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasPrincess Annewho took gold, proving her style credentials at the medal ceremony for the Eventing Team Final, pairing beige slacks and boat shoes with a boxy navy blazer, white button down and her famous, statement cycling shades.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.530543373492283e-31, \"text\": \"Eventing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Artistic Gymnastics Women's Team Final, which was dominated by Team USA, on July 30 drew in yet more Stateside stars.Natalie Portman, in a mustard skirt suit, joined Nicole Kidman, Serena Williams, Spike Lee and Bill Gates to watch on.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2790, \"end\": 2800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9974254362157565, \"rank\": 0.0025812087195180348, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp